Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.10,0:02:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.00,0:02:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我 拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.20,0:02:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}纠缠不休的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.40,0:03:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱 爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.60,0:03:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到了哦 爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.30,0:03:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 现在就去 婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.40,0:03:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.30,0:03:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H0000FF&}着魔的少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.20,0:03:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹰村家 家里没有人 请留言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.50,0:04:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷路的 迷路的 小猫咪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.80,0:04:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的家是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.00,0:04:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙 给我适可而止啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.00,0:04:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事了 凉子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.80,0:04:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 下次再敢过来就杀了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.90,0:04:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.60,0:04:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事了 凉子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.10,0:04:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和妈妈会保护你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.00,0:04:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.00,0:04:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凉子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.80,0:04:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}已予受理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.30,0:04:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.30,0:04:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们准备放任不管到什么时候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.90,0:04:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹰村先生 请冷静点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.70,0:05:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我女儿一年来被那个男人监视着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.30,0:05:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么还不把他逮捕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.10,0:05:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经在您家的周围加强了警备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.90,0:05:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再用不了多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.00,0:05:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我们至今提供了多少证据啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.50,0:05:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而到现在你们连那家伙的名字都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.10,0:05:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.10,0:05:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.40,0:05:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呦 抱歉 辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.90,0:05:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如月先生 怎么样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.00,0:05:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天他又出现了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.20,0:05:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉 我们也在着手进行处理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.00,0:05:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋元 不好意思 能不能去帮我买杯咖啡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.00,0:05:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值了夜班 困死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.10,0:05:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.00,0:05:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人的圈定差不多完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.00,0:05:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花了这么长时间真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.60,0:05:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说我们也遇到了不得不谨慎行事的情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.60,0:05:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.30,0:06:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位刑警吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.40,0:06:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是警察内部的犯罪行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.00,0:06:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的行动也会受到不小的限制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.70,0:06:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是那个秋元 是有权势人的儿子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.50,0:06:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果行事不慎 一切就都会被掩饰过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.60,0:06:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是刑警干的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.50,0:06:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会将他逮捕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.70,0:06:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过由于这些情况 不得不谨慎行事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.90,0:06:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在掌握确凿的证据之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.00,0:06:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就请您再稍微忍耐一阵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.00,0:06:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如月先生 我女儿已经忍到了极限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.70,0:06:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.00,0:06:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹰村先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.70,0:06:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.40,0:06:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋元回来了也请您装作不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.10,0:06:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不要摆出怀疑的态度 可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.90,0:07:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.00,0:07:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.20,0:07:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 警部 像平时一样黑咖啡就可以了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.20,0:07:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢谢 秋元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.20,0:07:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮你垫钱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.60,0:07:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这已经是第三杯的钱了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.10,0:07:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.70,0:07:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 来救救我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.15,0:07:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(550,160)\frz6}爱你啊\N\N凉子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.20,0:07:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凉子 怎么了凉子 凉子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.90,0:07:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.00,0:07:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家时我会再来接你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.00,0:07:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢谢爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.90,0:07:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心 有爸爸在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.40,0:07:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.70,0:07:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 你道什么歉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.40,0:07:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹰村同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.30,0:08:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2年A班的鹰村凉子同学吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.00,0:08:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.00,0:08:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能过来一下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.30,0:08:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.40,0:08:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 请进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.80,0:08:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.00,0:08:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.30,0:08:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.40,0:08:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.50,0:08:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你呼唤我的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.50,0:09:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阎魔爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.30,0:09:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.90,0:09:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于明白了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.30,0:09:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来救我了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.40,0:09:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呼唤我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.50,0:09:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.90,0:09:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样终于可以结束了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.20,0:09:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一年中你这么痛苦吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.70,0:09:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初是情书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.00,0:09:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都放进我家信箱里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.60,0:09:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来 又变成了奇怪的礼物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.40,0:09:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.50,0:09:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那很不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.60,0:09:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想要引起你的注意吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.70,0:09:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相当烦恼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.50,0:09:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.60,0:09:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断给我打电话和发邮件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.30,0:09:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我换了好几次邮箱都没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.60,0:09:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起的情报网啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.80,0:09:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后 更是发展到每天晚上都被跟踪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.40,0:09:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了最后 不知道怎么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.30,0:10:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在我家没人的时候进来我的房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.53,0:10:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs17}今天在街上见到很棒的衣服\N\N我想应该会很适合你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.90,0:10:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里的钥匙换了好几次也没有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.60,0:10:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经到极限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.40,0:10:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我 爸爸和妈妈更看不下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.90,0:10:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮入道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.00,0:10:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.50,0:10:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.30,0:10:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你若真的要消除怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.40,0:10:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将脖子上的红线解开即可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.10,0:10:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开绳线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.70,0:10:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和我正式缔结了契约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.80,0:10:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怨恨的人将立刻坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.50,0:10:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.70,0:10:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.80,0:10:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨若已消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.70,0:10:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自身亦将付出代价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.90,0:10:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.10,0:11:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害人终害己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.40,0:11:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缔结契约后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.30,0:11:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你亦将坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.80,0:11:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你死后的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.70,0:11:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法前往极乐净土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.90,0:11:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的灵魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.60,0:11:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将饱尝痛楚与苦难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.30,0:11:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远徘徊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.90,0:11:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.40,0:11:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.90,0:11:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后的事 就由你自己抉择了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.10,0:12:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.80,0:12:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.30,0:12:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法前往极乐净土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.40,0:12:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的灵魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.60,0:12:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将饱尝痛楚与苦难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.70,0:12:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远徘徊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.90,0:12:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.80,0:13:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死 死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.40,0:13:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思来晚了 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.60,0:13:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.90,0:13:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刑警先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.20,0:13:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经知道犯人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.10,0:13:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.00,0:13:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 现在就准备去逮捕他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.90,0:13:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\fs25\fn华文细黑}お家を聞いても　分からない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.90,0:13:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fad(200,200)}问你家在哪里你也听不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.20,0:13:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\fs25\fn华文细黑}なまえを聞いても　分からない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.20,0:13:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fad(200,200)}问你叫什么名字你也听不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.70,0:13:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\fs25\fn华文细黑}ニャン　ニャン　ニャン　ニャン
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.70,0:13:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fad(200,200)}喵 喵 喵 喵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.20,0:14:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\fs25\fn华文细黑}泣いてばかりいる　こ猫ちゃん
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.20,0:14:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fad(200,200)}一直哭泣的小猫咪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.40,0:14:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\fs25\fn华文细黑}犬のおまわりさん　困ってしまって
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.40,0:14:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fad(200,200)}狗巡查先生 束手无策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.10,0:14:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\fs22\fn华文细黑}ワン　ワン　ワン　ワン
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.10,0:14:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fad(200,200)}汪 汪 汪 汪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.30,0:14:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\fs22\fn华文细黑}ワン　ワン　ワン　ワン
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.30,0:14:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fad(200,200)}汪 汪 汪 汪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.70,0:14:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.00,0:14:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别大喊大叫啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.10,0:14:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要露出这么害怕的表情啊 凉子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.70,0:14:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有资格这样叫我的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.60,0:14:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.00,0:14:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是一直在交换礼物吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.90,0:14:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那完全是你单方面送来的不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.60,0:14:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找那些花 可是很辛苦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.20,0:14:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是你和朋友谈话时说过“好想要”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.50,0:14:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不用这么辛苦去找了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.30,0:14:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人偶也是 虫子也是 还有那漂亮的洋装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.30,0:14:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.50,0:14:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你生日时送给你的那个小仓鼠的尸体也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.50,0:14:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.10,0:14:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱一个人就是要尽心尽力呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.70,0:15:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我真的准备竭尽全力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.20,0:15:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.40,0:15:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这么爱你 你有什么不满意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.30,0:15:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 为什么 为什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.30,0:15:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有你的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.90,0:15:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不会有这么痛苦的回忆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.00,0:15:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.10,0:15:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么痛苦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.80,0:15:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的爱让你哪里痛苦了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.30,0:15:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.70,0:15:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凉子 我在问你痛苦什么了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.50,0:15:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你亦将坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.20,0:15:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再问你最后一次 凉子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.00,0:15:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪里让你痛苦了 哪里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.70,0:15:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 凉子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.40,0:15:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.30,0:15:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.10,0:15:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凉子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.60,0:15:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨 恨 已 闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.90,0:15:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.40,0:15:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.30,0:16:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有了 人偶没有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.90,0:16:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 凉子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.20,0:16:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契约已经签定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.50,0:16:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看你胸前吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.10,0:16:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是契约的刻印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.40,0:16:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契约的刻印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.30,0:16:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱 长衫放好了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.00,0:17:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.20,0:17:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.60,0:18:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅 你竟然背叛了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.20,0:18:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会要你好看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.80,0:18:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.20,0:18:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好到熄灯时间了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.60,0:18:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.10,0:18:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真头疼啊 这水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.70,0:18:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能这样啊 开着不关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.30,0:19:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.90,0:19:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗憾啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.20,0:19:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.50,0:19:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公 不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.90,0:19:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.40,0:19:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活该
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.50,0:19:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也马上就会追随你爸爸去了啊 凉子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.40,0:19:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是背叛我的报应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.80,0:19:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.00,0:19:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟敢让我女儿如此痛苦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.40,0:20:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 是不是感受到什么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.70,0:20:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对自己做的事有没有感到抱歉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.70,0:20:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如月警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.00,0:20:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.00,0:20:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并没有做什么坏事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.20,0:20:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.10,0:20:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有错的是凉子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.60,0:20:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛的一方才有错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.20,0:20:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是她的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.20,0:20:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了吗 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.50,0:20:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷失于黑暗中的可悲之影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.00,0:20:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤害鄙视他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.60,0:20:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉溺于罪恶的孽魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.80,0:20:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来死一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.00,0:21:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这里是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.80,0:21:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢 慢着 要把我带到哪里去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.50,0:21:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里到底是什么地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.00,0:21:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道呢 到底是那里呢 亲爱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.30,0:21:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要干什么 放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.60,0:21:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.30,0:21:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此怨此恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.10,0:21:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将流向地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.60,0:21:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷路的 迷路的 小猫咪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.60,0:22:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的家是在哪里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.80,0:22:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 不善交际的凉子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.10,0:22:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就罚她一个人 去幽灵公寓探险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.70,0:22:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 不要 我才不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.30,0:22:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么请我们吃饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.80,0:22:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.10,0:22:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是任性的小姐啊 嘿嘿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.80,0:22:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 明天见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.70,0:22:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 明天见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.60,0:22:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.20,0:22:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.00,0:22:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.60,0:22:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.50,0:22:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.40,0:22:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为道歉今天就去吃凉子喜欢的东西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.10,0:22:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这是个好主意啊 妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.90,0:22:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.60,0:22:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君之怨恨 愿为消之
